{"tid":1834744,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"之前好似聽聞共匪黨話2020年要全面脫貧","createTime":"2020-01-22T14:07:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-22T14:10:08.000Z","uid":231812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1814f3fe526074b3b62d30c94f0f0ad5078fee0f","tid":1834744,"uid":231812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T14:07:51.000Z","msg":"之前好似聽聞某共匪黨話2020年要全面脫貧.睇來呢次共匪黨一早打算捉緊機會.故意強硬封鎖消息<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />要一班窮人死.畢竟窮人冇財力防疫.佢地真係好撚想脫貧.咁我地就要反你啦.一旦攬炒.全共匪黨一齊陪葬.包括曱近平.但我新年願望好希望某共匪黨最高領導人都賴嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />.不如大大你親身走落去武漢個市場一轉.感受下病情.貼近下民意.然後再大大力咁.強硬地講止病制疫<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPS：記得唔好帶口罩.做個堂堂正正的中國人唷！親！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"439d11346f827c49155bc7c6e38505dcdde0ee51","tid":1834744,"uid":231812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T14:08:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"95ca8ded43b471b882c78be37fc6cc21a0fac9af","tid":1834744,"uid":231812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T14:08:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3fa454bd0bf25593132d2b8e994b1a8446680164","tid":1834744,"uid":231812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T14:08:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c18d7cc40348ea2d0aaa12f282ada47cdd271097","tid":1834744,"uid":231812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T14:09:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"96d37cb30d920763a986b066f720e4ae11af69a5","tid":1834744,"uid":231812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T14:09:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fff35519f5b2338fa0feb2779115af1cbf762519","tid":1834744,"uid":231812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T14:09:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"403923f70cc5ca1f1c579941dde2f914b719fae6","tid":1834744,"uid